BA_ "Description" SG_ 3221225472 L_3HKBD_Typ2 "Bit 0~1 (2nd Rear Auto Step):0 ? None/1 ? Single(On/Off)/2 ? 2 Step Type (High/Low/Off)/3 ? 3 Step Type(High/Medium/Low/Off)
Bit 2~3 (2nd Rear Mode Control):0 ? None/1 ? Single/2 - Dual/3 ? (RESERVED) 
Bit 4 (2nd Rear SYNC):0 ? None/1 ? SYNC
Bit 5~6 (";
